WEBVTT

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:33.850
Labda kwenye hatua hii,
unafikiri mimi ni mdhanifu?

00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:38.776
Nataka nikupe changamoto.

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.576
Kabla mwisho wa mwaka huu,

00:11:40.600 --> 00:11:45.296
nawaita kumkaribisha
mtu unaemuona mbaya --

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:49.376
mtu usiekubaliana nae
kisiasa na/au kiutamaduni

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:52.080
na unaefikiri hauna
chochote mnachofanana.

00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:58.090
Nawaita kualika mtu kama
huyo kwenye #mazungumzokahawa.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:00.990
Mnamkumbuka Ingolf?